    "en": "**A Refreshing Whiskey Cocktail**\n\nThe Lynchburg Lemonade is a modern classic, known for its:\n\n*   Easy-drinking nature\n*   Balanced sweet and sour flavors\n*   Refreshing, bubbly character",
